title: #71 - Chris D'Elia
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we're joined in the studio by actor and comedian Chris D'Elia! Together we discuss Logan Paul, Garth Brooks, La Croix, wiping techniques, and podcasting! Chris D'Elia is currently on his "Follow The Leader" national tour, and hosts the weekly "Congratulations Podcast with Chris D'Elia".
